NUMBER 2094
NAME Astral Plane
CHANNEL 84
REGION 50
ASTRAL
MONSTER_GROUP 90
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Floating in space like a platter, this flat land holds a luxurious and lush garden. Every variety of fruit, vegetable, tree, and plant known seems to grow here. A babbling brook appears at one corner and trickles out of sight on another. As you move past, down and under, you expect the roots to show though the paper thin surface, but when you try to look at its underside, you find the entire plane disappears.
*DESCRIPTION_END
