CEVENT 56 20 2086
ECHO ALL The voices of the pillared humanoids echo through the plane,%c   "We are the Keepers of Astral Harmony.%c    Do not betray our laws."%cThey then resume their soft murmuring.
AFFECT 2084
RANDOM DUMMY1 1 4 0
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
	ECHO ALL An insect like figure with a golden exoskeleton motions warriors forwards.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 2
	ECHO ALL A circle of red-robed wizards stand atop an open tower mouthing arcane chants.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 3
	ECHO ALL Weary farmers standing on an scraggly field, gaze up at a purple sky.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 4
	ECHO ALL With a slow ponderous movement, the statue points the scepter at one of the planets spinning about the throne. A loud noise fills the space, and in an blinding explosion the planet disintegrates into small pieces of rock. After a few moments the figure again points the scepter at the remaining rocks, and they reform into another, different looking planet.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 5
	ECHO ALL You recognize Ming K'tuk soaring above the Teeth of Shartaan.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 6
	ECHO ALL A small childs plucks a blossom from a weed.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 7
	ECHO ALL A butterfly is caught in the maw of a praying mantis.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 8
	ECHO ALL A robed being with a tenticled head pulls the supporting pole from a tent.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 9
	ECHO ALL A sun dies.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 10
	ECHO ALL A cell divides.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 11
	ECHO ALL A king takes a seat on a blue marble throne.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 12
	ECHO ALL A giant cube orbits a planet.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 13
	ECHO ALL A corpse rises as undead.
ENDIF
AFFECT 2090
ECHO ALL A four-armed humanoid, dressed in glimmering white robes, tends to an fallen warrior upon some distant battlefield.
AFFECT 2094
ECHO ALL In a dazzling display of light and beauty, a glowing star ascends slowly from one of the many pools dotting the garden. Dripping sparkling drops of water, the glorious star ascends to its proper place within the Astral firmament.
;
;
;
MLIST 90 371 100 9
MLIST 90 372 25 1
;
NUMBER 2099
NAME Everywhere
*DESCRIPTION_START
A great wind carries you through space with a roar.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFENTRY
	RECALC
	ECHO PLAYER You feel a powerful tug through your silver cord.
	EQUAL DUMMY1 DEPARTROOM
	IFVAR DUMMY1 = 0
		EQUAL DUMMY1 2099
	ENDIF
	KILL PLAYER
	POSITION LAY
	MOVE 1815
	AFFECT 1815
	ECHO OTHERS Suddenly a mysterious wind twists thought the cavern darkness picking up rocks and dust and hurling them through the air.
	DAMAGEALL CRUSH 10 You are hit by flying debris.
	ECHO OTHERS %N tumbles out of the whirlwind in a heap.
	IFVAR DUMMY1 ! 2099
		AFFECT DUMMY1
		ECHO ALL %N disappears with a pop!
		DAMAGEALL CRUSH 20 The ether explodes to fill the void!
	ENDIF
	AFFECT 1815
	PLREVENT 2
	CONTPLREVENT
	ECHO OTHERS The wind disappears as suddenly as it came.
	ECHO PLAYER Your silver cord fades away.
ENDIF
;
; Quasi Astral Rooms
;
NUMBER 2226
NAME Synaptic plane
region 120
channel 120
*description_start
multi-hued swirls of gray mist dance about you in an almost sentient
way. Your vision is almost totally obsured, but at times, the mists are
transluscent. Flashes of lightning-like energy flash and pulse almost
constantly. The feelings of hot and cold alternate in an attempt to
fool your senses. Off in the distance you hear an faint dripping sound
and well as some deep voices chanting.
*description_end
fixed_light
Astral
;mist
item 0 1230 val2=1672
extend 0 which dances and swirls
;
